      "id": 1,
      "options": {
        "content": "Use this view when latency rises but LLM/vendor panels do not explain it.\n\n- In-flight requests/streams show gateway saturation.\n- Goroutines and threads should scale with load and return after load drops.\n- Memory and GC separate heap pressure from RSS growth.\n- CPU and file descriptors catch local host/container resource limits.",
        "mode": "markdown"
      },
      "pluginVersion": "12.3.0",
      "title": "How to analyze runtime pressure",
      "type": "text"
    },
